{"tid":1874061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】世銀行長拒貸款助華抗疫 「中國本身資源充沛」","createTime":"2020-02-11T03:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T12:20:33.000Z","uid":28765,"like":710,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"4093e54c87ed29bcd8e32648a03be135347a7bf3","tid":1874061,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/iNxBN2ztbJYmuMdYtXmbXzXUDe0=/1024x576/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/C7E3LMNSAEXB6QFD36QUA5G44E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FiNxBN2ztbJYmuMdYtXmbXzXUDe0%3D%2F1024x576%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FC7E3LMNSAEXB6QFD36QUA5G44E.jpg&h=36001b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬爾帕斯拒絕以貸款方式助中國抗疫。<br />\n(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界銀行行長馬爾帕斯（David Malpass）周一表示，會向中國提供技術支援對抗武漢肺炎疫情，但不會有新貸款。<br />\n<br />\n馬爾帕斯向路透社表示，世銀正與世界衞生組織合作去支援中國，包括在醫療與衞生政策上提供協助，或者分享應對過去衞生危機的經驗，但無計劃向中國提供財政援助，認為中國本身已經資源充足。<br />\n馬爾帕斯指中國擁有龐大外匯儲備，此刻不會考慮向中國提供新貸款。<br />\n<br />\n馬爾帕斯去年獲美國總統特朗普提名為世銀行長，被視為世銀剋星，上任前曾多次抨擊世銀「花費高效率低」，直指世銀借貸方式存在舞弊，而且沒有實際惠及借貸國人民。他又認為中國經濟增長迅速，世銀已無必要向華借款。<br />\n去年12月，美國反對世銀繼續向中國提供每年10至15億美元（78億至117億港元）的低息援助貸款，但世銀沒有理會。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200211/QROKFJ2FEIT4KTFJMF37SIO4UM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200211%2FQROKFJ2FEIT4KTFJMF37SIO4UM%2F&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=2af14c05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200211%2FQROKFJ2FEIT4KTFJMF37SIO4UM%2F&h=545b99f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200211/QROKFJ2FEIT4KTFJMF37SIO4UM/</a>"},{"pid":"fbdb3d5a5f6c396bf55608d2c3171d9de15f32a5","tid":1874061,"uid":40171,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"In Trump We Trust"},{"pid":"fc64dfa2dc507ac31ed9f50a51d20aadc52af418","tid":1874061,"uid":155095,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8mvSFsn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8mvSFsn.jpg&h=312ef135&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"283d8da2011dd462dc97f8c490b390b3c394a32e","tid":1874061,"uid":30169,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"博唔到"},{"pid":"e6d5aa36fe2bbb9d5ed31eeb5b42b184487dec2f","tid":1874061,"uid":346806,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"去年12月，美國反對世銀繼續向中國提供每年10至15億美元（78億至117億港元）的低息援助貸款，但世銀沒有理會。<br />\n<br />\n點解？有呢條友做行長應該唔批先係<br />\n定其他人奶共？"},{"pid":"2705e6e0921b80886a7117e499eb174b6bed695e","tid":1874061,"uid":155095,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"quote":{"pid":"fbdb3d5a5f6c396bf55608d2c3171d9de15f32a5","tid":1874061,"uid":40171,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"In Trump We Trust"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2555000/2559599/2342343_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2555000%2F2559599%2F2342343_1024_1024.jpg&h=46aadde8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9ba00f0794ba65d0ad53582e4e88563deceb70d","tid":1874061,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551a8c30f09c727cde36439a63d69c33bf8958cc","tid":1874061,"uid":40171,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"p